[30;1m348 | [0m[35m * Polyfills inheritance for prototypes by allowing different kinds of[0m

[30;1m4202 | [0m[35m   users who have always used `createClient` to create a `MatrixClient`.[0m
[30;1m4203 | [0m[35m * `"Room"` events will now be emitted when the Room has *finished* being[0m
[30;1m4204 | [0m[35m   populated with state rather than at the moment of creation. This will fire[0m
[30;1m4205 | [0m[35m   when the SDK encounters a room it doesn't know about (just arrived from the[0m
[30;1m4206 | [0m[35m   event stream; e.g. a room invite) and will also fire after syncing room[0m
[30;1m4207 | [0m[35m   state (e.g. after calling joinRoom).[0m
